{
  "texts": [
    "These feature maps provide no additional guidance to the network for accurate classification.",
    "Moreover, the Grad-CAM and Grad-CAM++ algorithms generated attention maps which are illustrated in the first row of the figures from Figs. 11, 12, 13 and 14.",
    "The regions in 11 Example from the Grass scene from RSSCN7 dataset.",
    "The first row represents example of lowest channel features after the channel attention layers that considered as a low important feature maps.",
    "The second row represents example of highest channel features after the channel attention layers that considered as an important feature maps the feature map that are brighter indicate the regions that are more crucial for classification."
  ]
}